-Hachi, are you sure
your barrier will hold?

34
00:03:52,021 --> 00:03:54,654
-Actually, I'm not sure at all.

35
00:03:54,688 --> 00:03:55,154
-Hm.

36
00:04:07,921 --> 00:04:09,754
-Stop holding back.

37
00:04:09,788 --> 00:04:12,521
You still don't get it, do you?

38
00:04:12,554 --> 00:04:15,488
What are you afraid of, Ichigo?

39
00:04:15,521 --> 00:04:19,221
-I'm not afraid of you.

40
00:04:19,254 --> 00:04:21,188
-I'm going to give
you a little tip.

41
00:04:21,221 --> 00:04:22,888
Use your Bankai.

42
00:04:22,921 --> 00:04:24,288
-Shut up.

43
00:04:24,321 --> 00:04:25,588
-Just as I thought.

44
00:04:25,621 --> 00:04:27,254
You're scared that
every time you're

45
00:04:27,288 --> 00:04:29,154
forced to use your
Bankai against someone

46
