powerful like me, you're going
to lose control of your soul

47
00:04:31,688 --> 00:04:33,388
to that frightening
inner Hollow of yours.

48
00:04:33,421 --> 00:04:35,421
-I said shut up!

49
00:04:35,454 --> 00:04:38,088
-Dumb ass.

50
