Just looking at your
face pisses me off.

51
00:04:40,654 --> 00:04:43,154
You're so terrified
it's pathetic.

52
00:04:43,188 --> 00:04:45,888
That's fine with me.

53
00:04:45,921 --> 00:04:47,421
Fight scared if you want to.

54
00:04:47,454 --> 00:04:50,888
You don't have to use
your Bankai or Hollowfy.

55
00:04:50,921 --> 00:04:52,988
It'll save me some
effort while killing you.

56
00:04:53,021 --> 00:04:53,488
Your choice.

57
00:04:57,721 --> 00:05:00,388
-Think.

58
00:05:00,421 --> 00:05:02,621
How is she able to Hollowfy
without losing her sanity?

59
00:05:05,654 --> 00:05:07,721
How can she just
take her mask off

60
00:05:07,754 --> 00:05:09,954
and put it back on like that?

61
00:05:09,988 --> 00:05:11,954
I have to pay more attention.

62
00:05:11,988 --> 00:05:13,454
Watch her every move.

63
00:05:13,488 --> 00:05:15,788
Find out how she does it.

64
00:05:15,821 --> 00:05:18,688
That's why I came here.

65
00:05:18,721 --> 00:05:20,988
I won't use my Bankai.

66
00:05:21,021 --> 00:05:22,688
I'm not going to Hollowfy.

67
00:05:25,721 --> 00:05:30,054
I refuse to let him
control my soul.

68
00:05:30,088 --> 00:05:32,954
Never again!

69
00:05:32,988 --> 00:05:33,954
[fighting noises]

70
00:05:50,388 --> 00:05:51,321
[screaming]

71
