[maniacal laughter]

72
00:06:19,288 --> 00:06:20,854
-OK, that's enough.

73
00:06:20,888 --> 00:06:21,488
Well, Hiyori?

74
00:06:21,521 --> 00:06:22,554
Are you satisfied?

75
00:06:27,721 --> 00:06:31,088
You understand now,
don't you, Ichigo?

76
00:06:31,121 --> 00:06:33,588
Your Hollow can't be
suppressed just by simply

77
00:06:33,621 --> 00:06:35,354
focusing your mind
on stopping it.

78
00:06:35,388 --> 00:06:37,654
