it's a gag that never fails.

97
00:07:27,721 --> 00:07:28,788
This used to have them
rolling in the aisles

98
00:07:28,821 --> 00:07:29,821
back in the good old days.

99
00:07:29,854 --> 00:07:30,788
Look at my funny beard!

100
00:07:33,488 --> 00:07:36,721
