102
00:07:41,121 --> 00:07:42,088
[footsteps]

103
00:07:48,921 --> 00:07:50,354
-Rukia.

104
00:07:50,388 --> 00:07:51,821
It's you.

105
00:07:51,854 --> 00:07:54,288
Did you find my brother?

106
00:07:54,321 --> 00:07:57,621
-Sorry, I didn't find him.

107
00:07:57,654 --> 00:08:00,021
-I see.

108
00:08:00,054 --> 00:08:02,821
[crying]

109
00:08:02,854 --> 00:08:03,754
[music playing]

110
00:08:10,021 --> 00:08:15,288
I can't find any trace of
his spiritual pressure.

111
00:08:15,321 --> 00:08:17,688
Where did you go, Ichigo?

112
00:08:17,721 --> 00:08:18,254
Where are you?

113
00:08:25,821 --> 00:08:26,254
-Ichigo.

114
00:08:31,154 --> 00:08:35,554
-How could you make this
poor kid cry, Ichigo?

115
00:08:35,588 --> 00:08:38,421
What a worthless big brother
you turned out to be.

116
00:08:42,321 --> 00:08:43,254
[heavy breathing]

117
