175
00:10:33,121 --> 00:10:34,854
---you whine about our
training methods, dumbass!

176
00:10:34,888 --> 00:10:36,621
-Quit call me dumb
ass, snaggletooth!

177
00:10:36,654 --> 00:10:38,954
